race.description: The Elephant & Castle Hotel Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tough race. RATTLE'N'ROLL (1) resumes. Three runs last time in were all good, third to Surfin' Bird when fresh at Moe with that form working out very well since. He just missed at the run two back at this track and if he runs up to his best he should go close in a winnable maiden. FORCEOFONE (5) has been firmly in the market in two runs this campaign and can be forgiven for being well beaten at $1.90 last start at Pakenham when heavy rain fell throughout. He can bounce back here. OLIVIA ROSE (9) has placed in all four runs this time in, trying hard when just beaten at Moe last time out. She lands in a good spot here and can break through. ZUBBA STORM (6) ran a solid race on debut at Moe and should have taken plenty of improvement from that. He draws ideally and can measure up. ABBY'S CROSSWORD (7) is off a let-up and back in trip but her past two runs have been very good.
